      "Intro": {
        "synopsis": "Character Creation dialog for Avatar Dark UrgeThe Dark Urge is a mess, barely compos menti, horribly injured and pained, simultaneously in a deliriious giddy joyful state where they've been stripped down to their primal form: a prophet of the end, an avatar of pure murder. This should sound fearful of violence, and deeply relishing it at the same time.",
        "how_to_trigger": "Select the character as an avatar in character creation and click the button that plays their voiced character description"
      },
      "Healed": {
        "synopsis": "The Dark Urge is subject to a powerful healing spell (Heal) and recovers some lost memories.This is just the Dark Urge being told by the narrator about their past.",
        "how_to_trigger": "Cast Heal on the Dark Urge."
      }
    },
